    "texte_orig": "What[SP]is[SP]with[SP]Eikichi!?[SP]He's[SP]only[SP]planning[SP]to\ninvite[SP]girls![1205][U+000F][SP]I[SP]see[SP]right[SP]through[SP]his[SP]game!\nWhat[SP]a[SP]horndog!",
