    "_term": [
      4358,
      4354,
      4355,
      5169
    ],
    "nom_orig": "Jun",
    "texte_orig": "But[SP]he's[SP]planning[SP]the[SP]destruction[SP]of[SP]the\nworld--that[SP]has[SP]to[SP]be[SP]stopped[SP]at[SP]all[SP]costs.",
