    "texte_orig": "I've[SP]got[SP]no[SP]place[SP]in[SP]the[SP]sky.[1205][U+000F][SP]I[SP]lived[SP]on[SP]the\nsea,[SP]and[SP]I[SP]planned[SP]to[SP]return[SP]there[SP]in[SP]death.[1205][U+000F]\nEvolution[SP]doesn't[SP]interest[SP]me.",
